Class DialogFactory

java.lang.Object
  de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.view.dialog.DialogFactory

public final class DialogFactory
extends java.lang.Object

Factories are responsible for object creation and they know to to create them. Instead of spreading object creation all over the place, we hold it at one place. This helps in getting maintain benefits.
